file.name: openapi3.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.3
info:
  title: users API
  version: 0.0.1
servers:
- url: http://localhost:8080
paths:
  /openapi3.json:
    get:
      tags:
      - users
      summary: Download ./gen/http/openapi3.json
      operationId: users#/openapi3.json
      responses:
        "200":
          description: File downloaded
  /users:
    get:
      tags:
      - users
      summary: all users
      operationId: users#all
      responses:
        "200":
          description: OK response.
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: array
                items:
                  $ref: '#/components/schemas/CreateRequestBody'
                example:
                - birth_year: 2016
                  name: ci5
                - birth_year: 2016
                  name: ci5
              example:
              - birth_year: 2016
                name: ci5
              - birth_year: 2016
                name: ci5
              - birth_year: 2016
                name: ci5
              - birth_year: 2016
                name: ci5
    post:
      tags:
      - users
      summary: create users
      operationId: users#create
      requestBody:
        required: true
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/CreateRequestBody'
            example:
              birth_year: 2004
              name: nne
      responses:
        "200":
          description: OK response.
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/CreateRequestBody'
              example:
                birth_year: 2001
                name: t0q
components:
  schemas:
    CreateRequestBody:
      type: object
      properties:
        birth_year:
          type: integer
          example: 1947
          minimum: 1900
          maximum: 2022
        name:
          type: string
          example: 7pd
          minLength: 5
      example:
        birth_year: 1935
        name: ll4
      required:
      - name
      - birth_year
tags:
- name: users
  description: API for Users
